# SOMA-X body-model assets are large binary blobs (~822 MB total) that
# users download on first use via `python scripts/setup_soma_assets.py`,
# which delegates to `soma.SOMALayer` (HuggingFace-backed). Keep the
# directory pinned in git so `read_soma._resolve_data_root` can find it,
# but never commit the assets themselves.
*.npz
*.pt
*.npy
*.obj
MHR/
!.gitignore
